</code></synopsis>
<p>Looks up @filename inside the search paths of @script. If @filename
is found, its full path will be returned .</p><p>found.</p>

<table>
<tr>
<td><p>filename :</p></td>
<td><p>the name of the file to lookup</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><p>Returns :</p></td>
<td><p>the full path of @filename or None if no path was</p></td>
</tr>
</table>
